How to change the frequency of email notification to users?

Tainan
updated 20 days ago

follow


    The mobilize events send some notificativos via email to the users such as the last known activity in the events, the due tasks and the next appointments, for example.
  The mangares and clients themselves can alter the frequency of the email notifications

In order to do that, access the user profile:

- Colaborador user: click on your picture on the top right corner or access the colaborador users in Settings > my team.
- Client User: access the event homepage of the user and in the block users, click on the selected user picture.

Inside the User profile, click on notificativos and choose the frequency that you want him to receive notificativos, as shown in the picture below:
[image]
Done! Now the users will receive notificativos with a determine frequency.
